8208"},{"id":"5d3c68d5ca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛的请话是会上唯一一个官方毂刊模明了鼓掌的分具值的话，藏联新间机喜藏刊登遍种鼓掌的熟烈程度·中国人可能想表明：德管反封个人崇拜，他何的领荐人仍然得到了他何的尊敬。但这个鼓掌的热烈程度也清楚地表明毛的罐话的不同部分是受到了什摩的默迎。","index":6,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"10f2affd82","type":"paragraph","text":"有四鼓掌，我随意给它何了一个计分法","index":7,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"89266b136b","type":"paragraph","text":"4分","index":8,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"80aceb889d","type":"paragraph","text":"全体起立，长时间的熟烈鼓掌","index":9,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"33f02eeae7","type":"paragraph","text":"3分","index":10,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"3d25cb8802","type":"paragraph","text":"长时周的熟烈鼓掌","index":11,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"6672339242","type":"paragraph","text":"2分","index":12,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"db5c084101","type":"paragraph","text":"熟烈鼓掌","index":13,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"b3a003977e","type":"paragraph","text":"鼓掌","index":14,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"953c089518","type":"paragraph","text":"1分","index":15,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"0aa481120b","type":"paragraph","text":"用鼓掌计分法把毛的话初步分如下","index":16,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"d9f8f5b193","type":"paragraph","text":"字敷所估篇幅的","index":17,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId":"8fc4898208"},{"id":"a79414e6d4","type":"paragraph","text":"百分比","index":18,"publicationId":"2e01193c-d51e-17cc-8471-72d0d333a71f","articleId